mil.nga.giat.geowave.index

Class NullNumericIndexStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.index.NullNumericIndexStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumericIndexStrategy, Persistable

    public class NullNumericIndexStrategy
extends Object
implements NumericIndexStrategy
    This is a completely empty numeric index strategy representing no dimensions, and always returning empty IDs and ranges. It can be used in cases when the data is "indexed" by another means, and not using multi-dimensional numeric data.
